Comment: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我將‘球’投入了這片土地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.95,0:00:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,‘它’為了收集信息而活動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,光線 氣味 聲響 愉悅 悲痛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.77,0:00:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,受到這些形形色色的信息刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.94,0:00:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,變得能夠變化成各式各樣的形態
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,‘它’變成了少年的模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.71,0:01:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,踏上了旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.80,0:01:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,尼南那的少女 瑪琦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.27,0:01:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,她被選為鬼熊的活祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.61,0:01:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,卻在被送往儀式的途中逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,再經由瑪琦的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,‘它’獲得了新的刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.43,0:02:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,謝~謝~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,謝~謝~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.06,0:02:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,謝~謝~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,在充滿各種刺激的這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.78,0:02:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,‘它’彷徨的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,才剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.21,0:02:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 我又不是你的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,把手伸出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,來 拿好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好幼稚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,明明臉上沒有印記
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,說回來 你是從哪兒來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不是尼南那的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,長得也不像矢野目人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,難道說是傳說中的土岐人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我來給你起個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:05:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我想啊 既然你是不死之身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那就叫「不死之身」好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,「不死身」？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,叫「不死」怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,太老土了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那「小不」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,小 不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,閒得我都快要睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他們也太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪琦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,找到妳了 瑪琦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪琦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我這就去救妳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,小不 媽媽要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,大多數動物無法選擇自身生存的環境
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 為了適應環境 必須主動改變自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,特別是對於人類而言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,這種變化的預兆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是情感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.43,0:10:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪琦 妳在哪裡 妳去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 你看到過一個小女孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,長頭髮的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.59,0:10:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:10:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,去哪裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,來 把這個吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼 味道好怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,要獻祭的女孩都會吃這個東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,請全部吃完
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,說起來 瑪琦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才和妳在一起的那個 是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,看上去既不是矢野目人也不是尼南那人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,說是旅行者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,碰巧在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不要說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,早瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.69,0:12:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那人就是我們昨天看到的那個可怕的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那根本不是這世界上的東西 是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.67,0:12:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,大家！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是望風的嗎 怎麼來找我們了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,別再往前走了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我們被襲擊 已經死一個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,襲擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,對 被一隻熊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,熊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,牠身上的刺…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是鬼熊大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 鬼熊只是個傳說而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到的不會只是普通的熊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那可不只是隻熊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我們繞路直接去祭壇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你是認真的嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,又有怪物又有熊的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.54,0:12:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這太不正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我們回村子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,出發
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,她睡得很熟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.91,0:14:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:15:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這回的任務真累人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,也得報告矢野目族死了人一事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這是 什麼聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那是！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.05,0:15:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼熊大人祂… 真的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪琦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,妳！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不也挺好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,誘餌變成了雙份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好緊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,快醒醒！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪琦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這陋習…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,妳沒有必要遵守
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,妳可以選擇長大成人的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,把門關好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他被吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.24,0:18:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他好像 還在掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那到底…是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,難道是神的偉業嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:21:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪琦 瑪琦 瑪琦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪琦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,姐…姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.64,0:21:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以當做儀式成功 瑪琦已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,妳們明白這是什麼意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是死在這裡 還是活著 去我的國家生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.83,0:21:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,做個決定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.83,0:22:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪琦 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,活下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.76,0:22:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,帶回矢野目
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.93,0:22:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,全部
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.39,0:22:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,全部？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.39,0:22:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,小孩 熊 還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.98,0:22:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那匹狼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.11,0:22:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子餓了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.78,0:22:32.83,up,,0,0,0,,瑪琦 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.12,0:22:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.25,0:22:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,牠吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.02,0:22:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.65,0:24:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,做了早瀨的俘虜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.66,0:24:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,從鬼門關死裡逃生的帕蘿娜和瑪琦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.04,0:24:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,在矢野目那繁華的城市裡 謳歌生的喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.00,0:24:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,然而 早瀨針對擁有不死之身的不死開展的計劃
